Paper: hep-th/9404147

Date: 1994-04-23

Title: Exponential behavior of a quantum system in a macroscopic medium

Authors: Hiromichi Nakazato, Mikio Namiki, Saverio Pascazio

Comments: 8 pages, report BA-TH/94-170

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev.Lett. 73 (1994) 1063-1066

An exponential behavior at all times is derived for a solvable dynamicalmodel in the weak-coupling, macroscopic limit. Some implications for thequantum measurement problem are discussed, in particular in connection withdissipation.